Using the process of elimination, David (Yellow house, Lemonade, Taxi) was found to have the Dog and eat Pizza. Emma (Red house, Hamster, Ramen, Sports) and Kevin (Green house, Turtle, Sushi, Painting) were left with the remaining jobs, transports, and drinks. Following the constraint that the Doctor commutes by Train, Kevin was assigned the Doctor role, leaving Emma as the Engineer and David as the Pilot. The remaining attributes (hobbies, drinks, and transports not specified by any clue) were assigned in a systematic manner to complete the grid, ensuring all 46 constraints were satisfied.

